title: Check Out This Unseen Photoshoot Of Kareena Kapoor During Her Pregnancy
text:
Rashmi Daryanani Feb . 15 . 2017 
Earlier, it was revealed that Kareena Kapoor would be the brand ambassador for Sony BBC Earth , a global factual entertainment channel that’s making its way to India. And now, we have four exclusive photos from a shoot the brand did with the actress, when she was about four months pregnant. They’re calling her the “feel alive” ambassador and so each photo is intended to showcase her spirited personality.
